Waking up to the morning sunrise over mountains, Fourth of July fireworks (on the 3rd of July), and otters on the dock are just a few of the pleasures this home affords you. Newer appliances in Kitchen. Large style entertaining deck, recently repaired private dock. Fenced dog area for your pups, plus invisible fence, outbuilding with Washer/Dryer and outdoor shower. AC (mini split), if it gets too hot. L shaped dock to tie up your speedboat and/or other water toys. Excellent rental or summer home.

An exceptional chance to build a private residence nestled on 5.6 acres of tranquil land, conveniently abutting renowned Chuckanut Drive. With Oyster Creek, Chuckanut Drive, and Samish Bay as its picturesque borders, this property offers a serene retreat amidst nature, recreational opportunities, and breathtaking views. A short walk from the property, you'll find the acclaimed Taylor Shellfish Oyster Bar, an iconic local favorite with a stunning beachside setting. Additionally, the proximity to popular hiking trails such as Oyster Dome and Blanchard Mountain ensures that world-class outdoor adventures are just steps away.

La Conner Heights is a premier BYK built collection of high-end custom homes set in the heart of Historic La Conner. 360 degree views of the quilted farmlands, majestic Mt. Baker, stunning Cascade Mountains and the sparkling Salish Seas. 2635 sq ft of designer driven finishes throughout, soaring ceilings, walls of glass and a seamless flow of living spaces. Luxurious primary suite. Chef's kitchen with large island open to living room and infinity deck. Dedicated office with powder room. La Conner offers the best of Skagit Valley - a vibrant art scene, local artisans, boutique shopping and farm to table dining. Acclaimed marina with the San Juan Islands at your back door. Just a short drive to I-5. Easy access to Seattle and Vancouver BC.

Ten heavily forested acres with a creek running through in beautiful Skagit County. Property consist of two secluded five acre parcels. Let your imagination soar on the possibilities. No studies have been completed. Buyers Due Diligence Required.

Welcome to Brickyard Park a 55+ Community! This home is a 3 bed/1.75 ba single story townhome with over 24K in upgrades. It is one of only 2 of these plans bordering the park on a premium lot. It has a vaulted great room w/gas fireplace. Kitchen has upgraded white cabinets, gas range, dw, micro hood & quartz counters. Primary ensuite has a vaulted ceiling, wic, 2 sinks & a tile shower in the bath. LVP flooring & upgraded carpet. Comfort height toilets. Garage & walls are insulated for sound. Single car garage. The HOA maintains your yard, irrigation & fences. HOA owns fences. There is a covered rear patio w/ a gas hookup. Clubhouse has an almost 1 acre park w/a walking trail around it. There is a pickleball ct, horseshoes, & bocce ball.

Welcome to Bucko Estates a new legacy community! This home is the Grady plan with 3 bed/1.75 bath & a 3 car garage all on one level! The great room w/gas fireplace has LVP flooring and is open to the kitchen & dining room. The kitchen has 36 upper Alabaster cabinets with an Ember on Maple colored island, a gas range, and a walk in pantry There are double closets for extra storage off of the great room. The home has quartz countertops throughout the home! The carpet and lights are all upgraded. Laundry room. The primary bedroom has a vaulted ceiling. The ensuite bath has a tile floor & tile shower, double sinks, & a walk in closet. There is a covered patio out back. The yard is fully landscaped & the backyard is fenced.

HIDDEN GEM! Rare 1.18-acre level, buildable and subdividable lot in Skagit Valley. Located in desirable Blackburn Ridge in the City of Mount Vernon. This property is zoned R-1, 5.0 and offers up to 4 sizable lots. All utilities are in the street. survey, projected plat map, soils, and preliminary storm drain modeling have been completed. This project is ready for the savvy investor to finish it out. area comps show home prices from in the upper $800's! A Great project to add to your portfolio awaits!

Build Your Dream on Little Mountain! This is your chance to own one of the last remaining views lots on Little Mountain, dont miss it! Tucked into a peaceful and highly sought-after neighborhood, this property offers incredible views and the perfect canvas to build your forever home. Youll love being just minutes from top-rated schools, parks, and all the local spots that make this area so special. Whether you're into hiking, morning walks, or simply soaking in the beauty of nature, the nearby trails make it easy to enjoy it all. Utilities are conveniently located at the street, making the building process that much smoother. Dont let this unique opportunity slip away; this view, this location, and this lifestyle wont last long!

Discover affordable living in this well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bath home in a 55+ community. Situated on one of the park's largest lots, it features a great floor plan, two storage sheds, a carport. Close to shopping, hospitals, and activities. Don't miss this opportunity!

Experience the ultimate in coastal living with this exceptional home, offering breathtaking views of Burrows Bay, the islands, Olympic Mountains, & the picturesque marina. The main level features a seamless blend of hardwood & slate flooring, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with granite countertops, stylish tile backsplash, a center island, & a spacious walk-in pantry for all your culinary needs. The lower level is your private retreat, with a luxurious primary suite featuring a cozy sitting area, an indulgent jetted tub, and an expansive walk-in shower. Outdoor spaces abound, with double decks that invite you to soak in the views or unwind in the recessed hot tub on the lower deck.

Experience unparalleled luxury in this redesigned lock-and-leave condo featuring high-end custom finishes throughout. An impressive 80-foot mural by renowned artist Jennifer Bowman, adds a unique touch of artistic elegance. Nestled against a protected forest, this 1Bed , den & media room offers privacy & tranquility. The interior is adorned w/marble, metals, handmade glass & fine textiles, complemented by walls of custom DeWils cabinetry and lighting. The residence comes with luxurious designer furniture that convey with the sale. Enjoy seamless indoor-outdoor living w/ 2 expansive decks, perfect for entertaining. Outdoor enthusiasts, a trail to Washington Park, beach & boat launch is out your front door. A lifestyle for the discerning.

Spacious Rambler on a beautiful, flat, fully landscaped 1 acre lot, Space for RV / Boat Parking or add a shop. 3 Car Garage. Hybrid heat pump water heater, High Efficiency ductless mini splits provide both heating and air conditioning to the entire living area.

Nestled along the lower slopes of Mount Vernons Hillcrest neighborhood, this west-facing, partially wooded lot is situated right in the heart of Skagit Valley.
